theorem odd_even_sum_is_integer {x y j k : ℤ} (hx : x % 2 = 1) (hy : y % 2 = 0) (hj : j % 2 = 1) (hk : k % 2 = 0) :
  ∃ S p, S = x + y ∧ p = j + k ∧ p ∈ ℤ :=
begin
  use [x + y, j + k],
  split,
  { refl },
  { split,
    { refl },
    { exact ⟨j, k, rfl⟩ } }
end
